Serialize an R Object to a Raw Vector

Source: R/rxRaw.R
rxSerialize.Rd

Serialize an R Object to a Raw Vector

Usage

rxSerialize(x, type = c("qdata", "qs2", "base"))

Arguments

x

object to serialize

type

serialization type; one of "qs2", "qdata", or "base".

Value

raw vector

Author

Matthew L. Fidler

Examples
